verbose_text: XREF_BIBR The SNP1 rs10941679 risk associated g-allele was moderately associated with increased FGF10 mRNA expression in NBCS normal breast (p = 0.013, p corrected = 0.39) and breast tumors (p = 0.005, p corrected = 0.38) as well as in GTEx normal breast (p corrected = 0.02; XREF_FIG A and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A).
